Interface Set<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the object type
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSet, HashSet, TreeSet

    public interface Set<E>
extends java.lang.Iterable<E>
    The interface to be implemented by any class attempting to create a Set
    Author:
    Bilal Mohamad (bmohama)
